OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNgozi Fulani receives      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpersonal apology at Palace 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Lady Susan Hussey has given a personal 
OL,6, apology to Ngozi Fulani, after asking  
OL,7, her where she was "really from" at a   
OL,8, Palace reception.                      
OL,10,FLady Susan, a former lady in waiting,  
OL,11,Fmet black British charity boss Ms      
OL,12,FFulani at Buckingham Palace on Friday. 
OL,14,FShe offered her "sincere apologies for 
OL,15,Fthe comments... and the distress they  
OL,16,Fcaused", said Buckingham Palace.       
OL,18,FA statement said Ms Fulani had accepted
OL,19,Fthe apology and recognised the comments
OL,20,Fhad not been malicious.                
